title: 114: Our First Kiss Stories | Ear Biscuits Ep. 114
description:
Rhett & Link talk about their first kisses -- from what it was like for them to have their first kiss with the same girl to failed first kiss attempts, are joined by Becca & Ellie of the Mythical Crew to talk their first kisses, and cover a sample of Mythical Beast first kisses as submitted by listeners on this week's Ear Biscuits.

Listen to Ear Biscuits at: 

Apple Podcasts: http://apple.co/29PTWTM

Spotify: http://spoti.fi/2oIaAwp
